than in firs, as documented by previous studies. We believe that the development of such objective definitions accompanied by ready-to-use tools for data processing, analysis and visualisation will reinforce the discipline by contributing efficiently to standardise concepts and methodologies. {\textcopyright} 2011 Istituto Italiano di Dendrocronologia.},
